IMPORTANT LICENSE NOTES

This software is free to use in your applications and projects. However,
please note the following restrictions:

1. NO COMMERCIAL DISTRIBUTION
   You may NOT sell this software or derivative works (such as database
   adapters) as standalone products or services.

2. ATTRIBUTION FOR EXTENSIONS
   If you create database adapters, extensions, or similar migration tools,
   you must provide attribution to the original author.

3. FREE TO USE IN YOUR APPLICATIONS
   You CAN freely use this software as a library in your commercial
   applications without any attribution requirements.

================================================================================

QUICK FAQ

Q: Can I use MSR in my commercial application?
A: Yes! Use it freely in your web apps, APIs, internal tools, etc.

Q: Can I create a PostgreSQL adapter?
A: Yes, but you must include attribution and cannot sell it as a product.

Q: Do I need to mention MSR in my app's credits?
A: No, only if you create migration tools/adapters based on MSR.

Q: Can I fork MSR and improve it?
A: Yes, but keep the attribution and cannot sell it.

Q: Can my company use MSR internally?
A: Absolutely! Internal use has no restrictions.

